    <item>
      <title>General Info</title>
      <link>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/classes/general/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 20:47:31 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/classes/general/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;leveling-in-zuluhotel-omega&#34;&gt;Leveling in Zuluhotel Omega&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To reach a level in a class you will need to have at least the amounts shown in the table below.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Decimals will not count towards your level so if you have 74.9 in a skill it will count as 74.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To reach higher than level 4 you will need either skill items or get tomes to raise your skill caps.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You can also find stat potions to raise your stat caps.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bard</title>
      <link>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/classes/bard/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 11:47:31 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/classes/bard/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;skills-&#34;&gt;Skills-&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/begging/&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  &gt;Begging&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/cartography/&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  &gt;Cartography&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/discordance/&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  &gt;Discordance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/herding/&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  &gt;Herding&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/musicianship/&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  &gt;Musicianship&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/peacemaking/&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  &gt;Peacemaking&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/provocation/&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  &gt;Provocation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/skills/tasteidentification/&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  &gt;Taste Identification&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;bonuses&#34;&gt;Bonuses&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Bonuses in all their specialized skills.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Can use Book of Songs.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Can use Archaic book of Verses&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Gains dexterity and intelligence quicker.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Can use shepherd’s crook without mace-fighting, damage and hit chance will check for class level instead.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;penalties&#34;&gt;Penalties&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Can’t wear plate armor.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Can’t wear shields.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Can only cast circle 1 spells.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Gains strength slower.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;additional-info&#34;&gt;Additional info&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To fill up the Book of Songs you will need to buy Pen and Ink (Mapmaker NPC) and simply double-click it. Then target the song scroll and the Book of Songs you wish to scribe the song into.&#xA;To fill up the Archaic book of Verses you need to use the verse scroll by double-clicking it. Upon success it will automatically be added to the Verse book.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
